{"tid":1534513,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[反思]其實帶頭罷課嘅 唔應該係學生自發 而係老師！","createTime":"2019-09-03T04:31:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:56:35.000Z","uid":191532,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0fcf205572d1032a2254bae851bde27df086be6a","tid":1534513,"uid":191532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:31:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DJZg8cx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDJZg8cx.png&h=3938f7ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">呢個情況各個大專院校有，我相信中學都有</span></span><br />\n中學生作為年輕人，不論係屋企人、發夢、學業方面，已經承受左好多壓力，好多老師甚至等學生自發罷課繼而再等老師能夠有理由支持。<br />\n我知有好多老師都知支持呢場運動，既然如此作為成年成熟教育水平高嘅一小眾點解仲會猶豫應該點做。其實只要老師帶頭罷工，可能第一日唔多得一兩個，第二日有其他老師，甚至學生感受到原來唔係自己一個行尼條路，慢慢，慢慢，其實全民罷課唔係一件成功唔到嘅事。<br />\n我知老師帶頭罷課會承受更多壓力，例如輿論、教席，失敗嘅後果等等，但係比起而家抗爭者所承受嘅代價，真係唔可以試左先？真係要驚輸而一切照舊生活？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知道有好多有良心嘅老師都會睇連登<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 要爭氣呀<br />\n呢場仗唔係得我地年輕人打㗎</span></span></div><br />\n一個罷左兩日課見到情況欠佳嘅大專生上"},{"pid":"0b9935a36daff2580c24387ca8ed57c197dfbd5a","tid":1534513,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:31:26.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3061b2dd37546c876059a91b4c48d65e593ca56f","tid":1534513,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:31:51.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"33f93f316ae81426f5358449b4c8292632ba569b","tid":1534513,"uid":191532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:33:07.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"c5ed01377dcbb72fdc7adc6f7c99a381dbe9c3c1","tid":1534513,"uid":191532,"like":0,"dislike"